About our coworking

StanGher Coworking is a spacious space where everything disposes to productive work and contributes to finding the right and effective solutions.


The whole space is divided into coworking and recreation areas. At your disposal will be not only a workplace, but also soft sofas, board games, a library, a mini-kitchen and a general pleasant atmosphere of the interior.
